WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:14.514 --> 00:00:17.600 position:50% align:center
New Himuka has been
deceiving all of us!

00:00:17.684 --> 00:00:21.521 position:50% align:center
You should understand that
better than anyone else, Seto.

00:00:21.604 --> 00:00:23.857 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
What are you talking about?

00:00:23.940 --> 00:00:25.650 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
I'll ask you again.

00:00:25.734 --> 00:00:28.903 position:50% align:center
Are you involved in that
terrible research or not?

00:00:28.987 --> 00:00:32.198 position:50% align:center
[SETO] Research? This is the
first I've heard of it!

00:00:33.908 --> 00:00:36.828 position:50% align:center
Gemma. We're well
past talking now.

00:00:38.163 --> 00:00:39.664 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:00:39.748 --> 00:00:42.959 position:50% align:center
--[OSF SOLDIERS shout]
--[SETO gasps]

00:00:43.043 --> 00:00:45.378 position:50% align:center
How many of these
guys can there be?

00:00:46.546 --> 00:00:49.966 position:50% align:center
[gasps, groans]

00:00:51.051 --> 00:00:53.428 position:50% align:center
No choice. We'll just
have to fight back.

00:00:59.893 --> 00:01:01.144 position:50% align:center
[KAGERO]
Oh, dear...

00:01:01.227 --> 00:01:03.563 position:50% align:center
I think I'd rather
sit this one out.

00:01:05.273 --> 00:01:06.983 position:50% align:center
Stop! Please calm down!

00:01:07.067 --> 00:01:08.068 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:01:08.151 --> 00:01:09.903 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:01:09.986 --> 00:01:11.821 position:50% align:center
[FEMALE OSF SOLDIER A shouts]

00:01:13.031 --> 00:01:14.074 position:50% align:center
You okay, Kasane?

00:01:14.157 --> 00:01:16.076 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:18.078 position:50% align:center
What's going on here?

00:01:18.161 --> 00:01:20.038 position:50% align:center
I thought we were
on the same side.

00:01:22.499 --> 00:01:23.708 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:01:31.132 --> 00:01:31.925 position:50% align:center
Nagi!

00:01:32.008 --> 00:01:33.093 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:01:33.176 --> 00:01:36.680 position:50% align:center
We sure trained together
a lot, huh, Yuito?

00:01:36.763 --> 00:01:40.558 position:50% align:center
Heck, we even ran late on
induction day together.

00:01:40.642 --> 00:01:42.894 position:50% align:center
Wanna go a round
with me, Kasane?

00:01:44.521 --> 00:01:45.980 position:50% align:center
Nagi...

00:01:47.482 --> 00:01:52.487 position:50% align:center
♪

00:03:21.868 --> 00:03:24.412 position:50% align:center
What the hell's gotten into you?

00:03:24.496 --> 00:03:27.582 position:50% align:center
Tell the truth. Are you
with Major General Karen?

00:03:27.665 --> 00:03:30.502 position:50% align:center
C'mon, it's nothing
personal, Kasane.

00:03:30.585 --> 00:03:33.630 position:50% align:center
I've got no idea what the
major general is planning,

00:03:33.713 --> 00:03:36.383 position:50% align:center
but I'm not about to
betray his orders, either!

00:03:37.884 --> 00:03:39.260 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:03:41.054 --> 00:03:42.472 position:50% align:center
[OSF SOLDIERS grunt]

00:03:44.849 --> 00:03:46.059 position:50% align:center
[LUKA grunts]

00:03:47.477 --> 00:03:49.688 position:50% align:center
[LUKA]
Karen.

00:03:49.771 --> 00:03:52.023 position:50% align:center
It's always the same.

00:03:52.107 --> 00:03:54.192 position:50% align:center
You don't tell me anything!

00:03:54.275 --> 00:03:56.653 position:50% align:center
Do you think I'm helpless?

00:03:56.736 --> 00:03:58.196 position:50% align:center
That's right.

00:03:58.279 --> 00:03:59.364 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:02.283 --> 00:04:04.202 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:04:04.285 --> 00:04:05.995 position:50% align:center
A straight shooter like you

00:04:06.079 --> 00:04:08.373 position:50% align:center
betraying your
own team like this.

00:04:08.456 --> 00:04:10.542 position:50% align:center
It must've been
eating you alive.

00:04:10.625 --> 00:04:11.960 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA gasps]

00:04:12.043 --> 00:04:13.420 position:50% align:center
[SETO grunts]

00:04:13.503 --> 00:04:14.713 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:04:15.755 --> 00:04:18.383 position:50% align:center
I don't know what your
motivations are here,

00:04:18.466 --> 00:04:21.928 position:50% align:center
but are you sure this is
the path you choose?

00:04:22.012 --> 00:04:23.471 position:50% align:center
The truth!

00:04:23.555 --> 00:04:25.473 position:50% align:center
That's all I want!

00:04:25.557 --> 00:04:27.142 position:50% align:center
And nothing more!

00:04:29.227 --> 00:04:32.731 position:50% align:center
I hate this. Having to
battle my comrades.

00:04:32.814 --> 00:04:34.983 position:50% align:center
It makes me sick to my stomach!

00:04:42.449 --> 00:04:45.410 position:50% align:center
[KASANE grunts]
Why's he attacking us?

00:04:45.493 --> 00:04:49.164 position:50% align:center
[YUITO] I dunno, but he was
acting weird earlier, too.

00:04:49.247 --> 00:04:51.041 position:50% align:center
We talked about Naomi

00:04:51.124 --> 00:04:53.251 position:50% align:center
and he seems to think
she died in battle!

00:04:53.335 --> 00:04:54.085 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:04:54.169 --> 00:04:55.378 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:58.798 --> 00:05:00.342 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:05:02.719 --> 00:05:05.347 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]
Nagi, you were there that day!

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:07.349 position:50% align:center
You saw it with your own eyes!

00:05:07.432 --> 00:05:09.768 position:50% align:center
Think about it!

00:05:09.851 --> 00:05:13.772 position:50% align:center
Naomi is dead. That's the truth.

00:05:13.855 --> 00:05:16.566 position:50% align:center
But it's not!

00:05:16.649 --> 00:05:19.194 position:50% align:center
She transformed into an Other.

00:05:19.277 --> 00:05:23.156 position:50% align:center
[NAGI]
Mm. If that's what you think,

00:05:23.239 --> 00:05:25.950 position:50% align:center
then my only choice
is to eliminate you.

00:05:28.661 --> 00:05:32.582 position:50% align:center
[YUITO, KASANE grunt]

00:05:32.665 --> 00:05:34.918 position:50% align:center
[NAGI chuckles]

00:05:35.001 --> 00:05:37.379 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:05:41.257 --> 00:05:43.176 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:05:45.553 --> 00:05:47.263 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:05:47.347 --> 00:05:51.976 position:50% align:center
[NAGI shouts]

00:05:52.060 --> 00:05:53.853 position:50% align:center
Please, Nagi! Stop this!

00:05:53.937 --> 00:05:55.146 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:05:56.231 --> 00:05:58.066 position:50% align:center
[SETO, GEMMA]
Huh?

00:06:00.777 --> 00:06:01.695 position:50% align:center
What is this?

00:06:01.778 --> 00:06:03.863 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:06:03.947 --> 00:06:06.241 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
Yuito! Kasane!

00:06:08.993 --> 00:06:10.912 position:50% align:center
[KASANE, YUITO gasp]

00:06:10.995 --> 00:06:14.541 position:50% align:center
[shouts]

00:06:14.624 --> 00:06:15.834 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:06:18.878 --> 00:06:20.088 position:50% align:center
[KASANE, YUIOT gasp]

00:06:23.466 --> 00:06:25.135 position:50% align:center
Captain Seto, sir!

00:06:25.218 --> 00:06:27.012 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
Are you both alright?

00:06:27.095 --> 00:06:27.846 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Yes, sir!

00:06:27.929 --> 00:06:29.222 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
Good.

00:06:30.932 --> 00:06:33.560 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
His power's abnormally boosted.

00:06:33.643 --> 00:06:36.646 position:50% align:center
Nagi, what happened?

00:06:38.523 --> 00:06:41.443 position:50% align:center
[grunts]
Huh?

00:06:43.653 --> 00:06:45.989 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:06:47.991 --> 00:06:50.869 position:50% align:center
[NAGI] Why are you giving me
that look, Captain Seto?

00:06:50.952 --> 00:06:52.120 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
Trust me.

00:06:52.203 --> 00:06:55.081 position:50% align:center
If you kill Yuito,
you're going to regret it.

00:06:55.165 --> 00:06:57.167 position:50% align:center
That's why I won't let you.

00:06:57.250 --> 00:06:58.585 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:07:04.841 --> 00:07:06.760 position:50% align:center
[shouts]

00:07:10.972 --> 00:07:14.684 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:07:14.768 --> 00:07:15.685 position:50% align:center
Heh!

00:07:15.769 --> 00:07:16.978 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
Huh?

00:07:19.522 --> 00:07:22.734 position:50% align:center
[SETO grunts]
That's enough!

00:07:22.817 --> 00:07:24.527 position:50% align:center
--[NAGI chuckles]
--[KASANE, YUITO gasp]

00:07:28.531 --> 00:07:30.408 position:50% align:center
What? No...

00:07:33.912 --> 00:07:35.622 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:07:37.707 --> 00:07:40.460 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
It's not over...

00:07:40.543 --> 00:07:41.961 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:07:43.254 --> 00:07:46.716 position:50% align:center
[SETO]
I still... have some strength.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.843 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:48.927 --> 00:07:50.762 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:07:57.185 --> 00:07:58.311 position:50% align:center
Nagi.

00:07:58.395 --> 00:08:02.691 position:50% align:center
Remember... you're part
of my platoon.

00:08:02.774 --> 00:08:06.361 position:50% align:center
And I'll never let
you switch sides.

00:08:06.444 --> 00:08:10.532 position:50% align:center
[NAGI groans]

00:08:12.826 --> 00:08:15.370 position:50% align:center
[SETO exhales]

00:08:15.453 --> 00:08:19.124 position:50% align:center
Nagi... Captain Seto.

00:08:21.626 --> 00:08:22.794 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:08:22.877 --> 00:08:25.046 position:50% align:center
[WAKANA] You must never
allow the Red Strings

00:08:25.130 --> 00:08:28.049 position:50% align:center
to escape your grasp.

00:08:28.133 --> 00:08:29.342 position:50% align:center
[WATARU]
What the--?

00:08:31.011 --> 00:08:32.679 position:50% align:center
Wataru! What's wrong?

00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:33.972 position:50% align:center
[WATARU]
How should I know?

00:08:34.055 --> 00:08:36.266 position:50% align:center
I've never seen
anything like this!

00:08:36.349 --> 00:08:37.934 position:50% align:center
[OSF SOLDIERS murmur]

00:08:38.018 --> 00:08:39.853 position:50% align:center
[SHIDEN]
Huh?

00:08:39.936 --> 00:08:41.688 position:50% align:center
What's up? Are you hurt?

00:08:41.771 --> 00:08:43.356 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:45.275 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
What is this feeling?

00:08:46.317 --> 00:08:49.070 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:08:49.154 --> 00:08:54.159 position:50% align:center
[KASANE, YUITO grunting]

00:09:01.332 --> 00:09:02.667 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]

00:09:02.751 --> 00:09:05.003 position:50% align:center
You guys. What's that?

00:09:15.930 --> 00:09:17.432 position:50% align:center
[OSF SOLDIERS gasp]

00:09:17.515 --> 00:09:21.144 position:50% align:center
[OSF SOLDIERS yell]

00:09:21.227 --> 00:09:23.021 position:50% align:center
[FEMALE OSF SOLDIER A]
Help us!

00:09:24.272 --> 00:09:26.691 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]

00:09:26.775 --> 00:09:28.735 position:50% align:center
Yuito! Run away!

00:09:32.489 --> 00:09:33.865 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]

00:09:35.825 --> 00:09:39.079 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]
Where'd he go? He's gone!

00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:40.288 position:50% align:center
[TSUGUMI]
Let's run. Now!

00:09:40.372 --> 00:09:44.584 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]
Yuito! Kasane!

00:09:44.668 --> 00:09:45.960 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:10:17.617 --> 00:10:19.619 position:50% align:center
[FEMALE OSF SOLDIER A gasps]
Help me!

00:10:19.703 --> 00:10:22.330 position:50% align:center
[MALE OSF SOLDIER A]
Commander, do something!

00:10:22.414 --> 00:10:24.624 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:10:31.631 --> 00:10:34.134 position:50% align:center
It seems it's finally arrived.

00:10:35.093 --> 00:10:37.512 position:50% align:center
[gasps, grunts]

00:10:41.933 --> 00:10:44.310 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
Seto!

00:10:44.394 --> 00:10:45.562 position:50% align:center
[HANABI, TSUGUMI gasp]

00:10:45.645 --> 00:10:47.063 position:50% align:center
No!

00:10:47.147 --> 00:10:48.356 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
Gemma?

00:10:50.734 --> 00:10:52.318 position:50% align:center
You saved them, Colonel.

00:10:52.402 --> 00:10:55.030 position:50% align:center
[LUKA grunts, gasps]

00:10:55.113 --> 00:10:56.781 position:50% align:center
[HANABI yells]

00:11:01.286 --> 00:11:04.706 position:50% align:center
[TSUGUMI gasps]
Hang on tight!

00:11:04.789 --> 00:11:09.336 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:11:11.838 --> 00:11:13.298 position:50% align:center
Seto!

00:11:15.675 --> 00:11:17.010 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:11:23.183 --> 00:11:26.269 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
No... I'm sorry!

00:11:30.565 --> 00:11:33.651 position:50% align:center
[LUKA pantss]

00:11:33.735 --> 00:11:35.695 position:50% align:center
[HANABI grunts]

00:11:35.779 --> 00:11:39.115 position:50% align:center
Wait a minute.
We're still alive?

00:11:39.199 --> 00:11:41.785 position:50% align:center
Sorry but we can't
celebrate just yet.

00:11:49.751 --> 00:11:52.003 position:50% align:center
[ALL gasp]

00:11:52.087 --> 00:11:53.630 position:50% align:center
Where's Captain Seto?

00:11:53.713 --> 00:11:55.507 position:50% align:center
That thing took him.

00:11:55.590 --> 00:11:58.551 position:50% align:center
Plus Yuito... And Kasane, too.

00:11:58.635 --> 00:12:00.053 position:50% align:center
[ALL gasp]

00:12:19.114 --> 00:12:21.825 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:12:21.908 --> 00:12:25.328 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Huh? What the--?

00:12:25.412 --> 00:12:27.414 position:50% align:center
Kasane!

00:12:27.497 --> 00:12:29.666 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:12:29.749 --> 00:12:30.959 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:12:45.140 --> 00:12:46.057 position:50% align:center
[KASANE grunts]

00:12:46.141 --> 00:12:48.560 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]
You all right?

00:12:48.643 --> 00:12:52.981 position:50% align:center
[KASANE exhales]
Not really.

00:12:53.064 --> 00:12:55.817 position:50% align:center
This place is... so weird.

00:13:11.332 --> 00:13:13.335 position:50% align:center
--[YUITO] Huh?
--[KASANE gasps]

00:13:13.418 --> 00:13:15.045 position:50% align:center
[KASANE]
Who's that?

00:13:15.128 --> 00:13:16.504 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Dunno.

00:13:16.588 --> 00:13:19.758 position:50% align:center
But he's got the Sumeragi
family crest on his uniform.

00:13:21.468 --> 00:13:25.430 position:50% align:center
[YUITO] Actually, he looks
just like Yakumo Sumeragi.

00:13:27.265 --> 00:13:28.475 position:50% align:center
[KASANE, YUITO gasp]

00:13:38.443 --> 00:13:39.652 position:50% align:center
[KASANE, YUITO gasp]

00:13:44.449 --> 00:13:48.119 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:13:51.873 --> 00:13:54.751 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:13:54.834 --> 00:13:58.296 position:50% align:center
Just like... in my dreams.

00:14:01.841 --> 00:14:03.051 position:50% align:center
Kasane!

00:14:08.264 --> 00:14:10.975 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]
Kasane!

00:14:11.059 --> 00:14:13.687 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
Yuito! Thank goodness!

00:14:13.770 --> 00:14:16.231 position:50% align:center
We got you back!

00:14:16.314 --> 00:14:17.565 position:50% align:center
[HANABI whimpering]
For a second,

00:14:17.649 --> 00:14:21.069 position:50% align:center
I was afraid that thing
swallowed you up forever.

00:14:21.152 --> 00:14:22.487 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:14:31.871 --> 00:14:34.874 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]
The team! Are they--?

00:14:34.958 --> 00:14:37.002 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
We're not sure.

00:14:37.085 --> 00:14:38.128 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:14:38.211 --> 00:14:41.589 position:50% align:center
[TSUGUMI]
No. You can't help them now.

00:14:41.673 --> 00:14:42.841 position:50% align:center
We were lucky.

00:14:42.924 --> 00:14:46.386 position:50% align:center
If we hadn't had Luka's
help, we'd be gone, too.

00:14:46.469 --> 00:14:47.846 position:50% align:center
Wait, Luka?

00:14:47.929 --> 00:14:50.473 position:50% align:center
[HANABI] He said he would
go find Major General Karen,

00:14:50.557 --> 00:14:53.768 position:50% align:center
and then he just ran off.

00:14:53.852 --> 00:14:55.061 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:14:58.481 --> 00:15:01.526 position:50% align:center
So you're still in
one piece. I'm glad.

00:15:01.609 --> 00:15:02.819 position:50% align:center
[YUITO exhales]

00:15:02.902 --> 00:15:05.655 position:50% align:center
[HANABI sighs] You're not
on their side anymore.

00:15:05.739 --> 00:15:07.282 position:50% align:center
Right, Gemma?

00:15:07.365 --> 00:15:09.242 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA sighs]
That's right.

00:15:09.325 --> 00:15:11.911 position:50% align:center
I believe that I've made
a terrible mistake.

00:15:11.995 --> 00:15:13.163 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]

00:15:13.246 --> 00:15:13.997 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Gemma!

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:17.167 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA groans]

00:15:17.250 --> 00:15:20.253 position:50% align:center
[alarm buzzes]

00:15:20.337 --> 00:15:22.797 position:50% align:center
[crowd chatters]

00:15:22.881 --> 00:15:24.215 position:50% align:center
Oh my gosh.

00:15:24.299 --> 00:15:26.968 position:50% align:center
After they give us the
all-clear, let's try this store!

00:15:27.052 --> 00:15:30.430 position:50% align:center
Sounds like fun! So what
time do they open up?

00:15:30.513 --> 00:15:32.557 position:50% align:center
Let's... see...

00:15:32.640 --> 00:15:33.433 position:50% align:center
Uh-oh.

00:15:33.516 --> 00:15:34.351 position:50% align:center
[WOMAN A]
Huh?

00:15:34.434 --> 00:15:35.435 position:50% align:center
That's odd.

00:15:35.518 --> 00:15:36.978 position:50% align:center
[WOMAN C]
Psynet's not working?

00:15:37.062 --> 00:15:38.897 position:50% align:center
--[WOMAN D] No way!
--[MAN A] This sucks!

00:15:38.980 --> 00:15:40.065 position:50% align:center
[MAN B]
The screen won't load!

00:15:40.148 --> 00:15:41.483 position:50% align:center
[WOMAN A, B gasp]

00:15:44.402 --> 00:15:47.822 position:50% align:center
It's a good thing we weren't
far away from a shelter.

00:15:47.906 --> 00:15:49.115 position:50% align:center
That should do it.

00:15:50.658 --> 00:15:53.328 position:50% align:center
You bandage wounds
like an old pro.

00:15:53.411 --> 00:15:56.456 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah. I was always
kind of sickly as a kid,

00:15:56.539 --> 00:15:58.500 position:50% align:center
and really fragile.

00:15:58.583 --> 00:16:01.586 position:50% align:center
So I'd patch myself
up when I got hurt.

00:16:01.670 --> 00:16:05.590 position:50% align:center
You're handy! I can't
do anything like that.

00:16:05.674 --> 00:16:08.593 position:50% align:center
Even though my uncle's in
charge of the OSF Hospital.

00:16:11.596 --> 00:16:13.264 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Here, you should take these.

00:16:13.348 --> 00:16:15.058 position:50% align:center
They'll help keep
your fever down.

00:16:16.142 --> 00:16:17.310 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
Thank you.

00:16:20.188 --> 00:16:21.856 position:50% align:center
I don't get it.

00:16:21.940 --> 00:16:23.233 position:50% align:center
[HANABI, YUITO, GEMMA]
Huh?

00:16:23.316 --> 00:16:24.984 position:50% align:center
How can you guys just
sit there talking

00:16:25.068 --> 00:16:26.611 position:50% align:center
as though nothing happened?

00:16:26.695 --> 00:16:27.987 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
Tsugumi...

00:16:28.071 --> 00:16:31.616 position:50% align:center
You might forgive Gemma,
but I still can't!

00:16:31.700 --> 00:16:34.577 position:50% align:center
We lost Commander
Seto in that fight,

00:16:34.661 --> 00:16:37.122 position:50% align:center
and Gemma was complicit.

00:16:37.205 --> 00:16:40.625 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA grunts]
She's absolutely right.

00:16:40.709 --> 00:16:44.254 position:50% align:center
We deserve to know.
What the hell was all that?

00:16:44.337 --> 00:16:47.340 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA exhales, inhales]

00:16:47.424 --> 00:16:49.342 position:50% align:center
It's New Himuka.

00:16:49.426 --> 00:16:51.636 position:50% align:center
They're creating a
surveillance state.

00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:54.389 position:50% align:center
The plan is to
center it in Suoh.

00:16:54.472 --> 00:16:56.057 position:50% align:center
What do you mean?

00:16:57.308 --> 00:17:00.603 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] First, the government
conducts medical exams.

00:17:00.687 --> 00:17:02.814 position:50% align:center
The intent is to use
the data to pinpoint

00:17:02.897 --> 00:17:06.359 position:50% align:center
the exact psionics users
they're going to need.

00:17:06.443 --> 00:17:10.780 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] Anyone scouted by the
OSF is unable to refuse.

00:17:10.864 --> 00:17:12.240 position:50% align:center
Once inducted,

00:17:12.323 --> 00:17:16.161 position:50% align:center
their growth is suppressed
to maintain their abilities.

00:17:16.244 --> 00:17:19.289 position:50% align:center
Growth suppression.
That's no secret.

00:17:19.372 --> 00:17:20.957 position:50% align:center
Exactly.

00:17:21.041 --> 00:17:24.294 position:50% align:center
And it's something that must be
done for us to defeat Others.

00:17:24.377 --> 00:17:27.255 position:50% align:center
I'm fine with that part.

00:17:27.339 --> 00:17:31.176 position:50% align:center
But... it doesn't stop there.

00:17:31.259 --> 00:17:34.220 position:50% align:center
There's personality
rehabilitation, too.

00:17:34.304 --> 00:17:35.096 position:50% align:center
--Huh?
--[TSUGUMI gasps]

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:36.598 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
Hm?

00:17:36.681 --> 00:17:39.351 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] I once had a comrade
who suddenly started acting

00:17:39.434 --> 00:17:41.728 position:50% align:center
like a different person.

00:17:41.811 --> 00:17:44.022 position:50% align:center
He'd always been
a critical guy,

00:17:44.105 --> 00:17:47.025 position:50% align:center
and when he changed,
everyone said,

00:17:47.108 --> 00:17:50.695 position:50% align:center
"It's like his personality's
been manipulated."

00:17:50.779 --> 00:17:52.739 position:50% align:center
Really?

00:17:52.822 --> 00:17:56.242 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] You new recruits
probably haven't heard about it,

00:17:56.326 --> 00:17:59.371 position:50% align:center
but this has been
done over and over.

00:17:59.454 --> 00:18:02.874 position:50% align:center
Personality rehabilitation is
somewhat of an open secret

00:18:02.957 --> 00:18:06.211 position:50% align:center
among members of the OSF.

00:18:06.294 --> 00:18:10.215 position:50% align:center
Well, you probably knew
about it, didn't you?

00:18:10.298 --> 00:18:12.133 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:18:12.217 --> 00:18:13.593 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:18:13.677 --> 00:18:15.887 position:50% align:center
This is all done under the
government's direction,

00:18:15.970 --> 00:18:17.889 position:50% align:center
--of course.
--[YUITO gasps]

00:18:17.972 --> 00:18:20.725 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] When I saw
Nagi's behavior, I knew.

00:18:20.809 --> 00:18:22.644 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
No way.

00:18:25.146 --> 00:18:27.732 position:50% align:center
[inaudible]

00:18:27.816 --> 00:18:29.442 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:18:29.526 --> 00:18:32.278 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
I'm actually 54 years old.

00:18:32.362 --> 00:18:34.030 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:18:34.114 --> 00:18:35.907 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA] The effects
of growth suppression 

00:18:35.990 --> 00:18:37.909 position:50% align:center
gradually wear off.

00:18:37.992 --> 00:18:42.706 position:50% align:center
Your body starts aging, and your
psionics begin to decline.

00:18:42.789 --> 00:18:46.292 position:50% align:center
One day, I'll have
to leave the OSF.

00:18:46.376 --> 00:18:50.714 position:50% align:center
But before that happens,
I wanted to find out the truth!

00:18:51.881 --> 00:18:55.635 position:50% align:center
Then I heard from Karen
that Seto was involved

00:18:55.719 --> 00:18:59.305 position:50% align:center
with the research on
personality rehab.

00:18:59.389 --> 00:19:03.685 position:50% align:center
But that can't be true.
It just doesn't sound like him.

00:19:03.768 --> 00:19:08.606 position:50% align:center
Right. Why did I let myself
believe something like that?

00:19:08.690 --> 00:19:11.735 position:50% align:center
I was... stupid.

00:19:14.154 --> 00:19:16.531 position:50% align:center
Okay, so, the major general.

00:19:16.614 --> 00:19:19.951 position:50% align:center
Is he against what the
government's been up to?

00:19:20.035 --> 00:19:21.244 position:50% align:center
No.

00:19:24.372 --> 00:19:26.708 position:50% align:center
It seems it's finally arrived.

00:19:30.128 --> 00:19:32.130 position:50% align:center
Karen's mysterious.

00:19:32.213 --> 00:19:34.966 position:50% align:center
Whatever he's after...

00:19:35.050 --> 00:19:37.093 position:50% align:center
...no one can be sure.

00:19:53.568 --> 00:19:57.906 position:50% align:center
[OTHERS groan]

00:20:00.116 --> 00:20:01.326 position:50% align:center
[KAITO]
Hm?

00:20:02.744 --> 00:20:04.287 position:50% align:center
[KAITO'S SUBORDINATE A]
Chief Sumeragi!

00:20:06.414 --> 00:20:07.791 position:50% align:center
There's a swarm of Others!

00:20:07.874 --> 00:20:10.335 position:50% align:center
They've just advanced
into the heart of Suoh!

00:20:10.418 --> 00:20:13.922 position:50% align:center
Others? Then have them
exterminated post-haste!

00:20:14.005 --> 00:20:15.173 position:50% align:center
[KAITO'S SUBORDINATE A]
But I can't, sir.

00:20:15.256 --> 00:20:16.925 position:50% align:center
The defense system
is inoperable!

00:20:17.008 --> 00:20:18.968 position:50% align:center
Psynet isn't working!

00:20:19.052 --> 00:20:21.221 position:50% align:center
[KAITO gasps]
And the council?

00:20:21.304 --> 00:20:22.180 position:50% align:center
[KAITO'S SUBORDINATE A]
I don't know!

00:20:22.263 --> 00:20:24.140 position:50% align:center
There's no way to contact them.

00:20:24.224 --> 00:20:25.684 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:25.767 --> 00:20:28.978 position:50% align:center
[KAITO]
So, then. Arahabaki must be...

00:20:35.819 --> 00:20:38.905 position:50% align:center
Karen, why would you do this?

00:20:40.031 --> 00:20:44.703 position:50% align:center
[OTHERS grunting]

00:20:51.960 --> 00:20:55.880 position:50% align:center
This time, for certain.
I'll get it back.

00:21:03.763 --> 00:21:05.807 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA]
Kasane, speak to me!

00:21:07.392 --> 00:21:09.936 position:50% align:center
[KASANE grunts]

00:21:11.229 --> 00:21:12.439 position:50% align:center
You're awake!

00:21:13.732 --> 00:21:17.360 position:50% align:center
[KASANE grunts]

00:21:21.865 --> 00:21:24.909 position:50% align:center
[KASANE]
Was all that... just a dream?

00:21:24.993 --> 00:21:28.079 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA]
Poor thing. Are you okay?

00:21:28.163 --> 00:21:29.539 position:50% align:center
[KASANE]
Yeah.

00:21:32.834 --> 00:21:34.502 position:50% align:center
[KASANE]
Where are we?

00:21:34.586 --> 00:21:37.172 position:50% align:center
[ARASHI]
Kasane, check that out.

00:21:37.255 --> 00:21:38.465 position:50% align:center
[KASANE gasps]

00:21:46.097 --> 00:21:48.224 position:50% align:center
Isn't that the Kunad Highway?

00:21:48.308 --> 00:21:50.060 position:50% align:center
What happened to it?

00:21:51.144 --> 00:21:52.103 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA gasps]

00:21:52.187 --> 00:21:54.647 position:50% align:center
Everyone's as surprised
as you are.

00:21:54.731 --> 00:21:58.276 position:50% align:center
We woke up and it
was just like that.

00:21:58.360 --> 00:21:59.569 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:22:18.755 --> 00:22:21.966 position:50% align:center
[MAN A] There's not
much time, Kasane.

00:22:27.555 --> 00:22:32.560 position:50% align:center
♪